locality: Puntarenas/Limon Border, Cordillera de Talamanca, between Cerro Kasir and Cerro Nai; continental divide.

Prov. San José and Cartago. Montane forest formation with open landslides and road cuts and small swamps, about 22 km. southeast of Empalme, along the Interamerican Highway. In a moist depression below (west of) the summit of the highway at about 3100 m. alt.
R.B. Cerro Las Vueltas. Cuenca del Pirrís-Damas. Dota. R. B. Cerro Las Vueltas. 2 kilometers of entrance.
Cartago/San José Province Border: Ca 15 km south-southeast of the El Empalme Intersection on the Cordillera de Talamanca
Parque Nacional La Amistad. Cerro Fábrega. Low forest on steep east facing caribbean slopes of Cerro Fábrega, dominated by oak, ferns, mosses, epiphytes.
Cerro de la Muerte. Montane forest formation with open landslides and road cuts and small swamps, about 22 km. southeast of Empalme, along the Interamerican Highway. Prov. San José and Cartago.
